    "notes": "Core file model (FileModel<T>) and config model (ConfigModel<T>) are ported with simplified Rust-idiomatic APIs. The emRec serialization system is replaced by a Record trait using KDL format. ResourceCache provides emRes-like caching. OS/threading utilities (emThread, emProcess, emMiniIpc, emTmpFile, emFileStream) are not_applicable as Rust std provides equivalents and the app is single-threaded. Complex UI components (emFilePanel, emFileDialog, emFileSelectionBox, emCoreConfigPanel, emTunnel) and plugin systems (emFpPlugin) are not_ported. emCoreConfig fields are hardcoded in Rust rather than configurable."
